title: 09/20: Start or Sit (AFC); Buy High Candidates (Fantasy Football Podcast)
description:
We always talk buy low/sell high, but what about players to buy high (1:00)? We've got some names for you at the top of the show before getting into Start or Sit. How are we ranking Ryan Fitzpatrick this week (6:33)? Which key NFL injuries could have a Fantasy impact in Week 3 (12:00)? ... Debating Giovani Bernard vs. David Johnson (18:30) and a bonus Fantasy Regulators (22:55) that sparks a debate ... DEN-BAL (25:30), SF-KC (34:01), OAK-MIA (39:20), NYG-HOU (46:00), PIT-TB (50:45), TEN-JAC (55:20), NE-DET (59:30) ... Your emails at fantasyfootball@cbsi.com
